headline: Political Third Wheel Makes the Most of It
abstract: In an unusual diplomatic moment, President Trump met with both Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu of Israel and his challenger, Benny Gantz, on the eve of releasing a Middle East peace plan.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — For Benny Gantz, the leader of the centrist Blue and White Party in Israel, traveling to Washington on Monday to meet with President Trump at the same time as the man he is trying to defeat wasn’t exactly a state visit.
